## Amazon Web Service(AWS)

## Instance : 
Virtual server for running applications on amazon EC2

## EC2(Elastic Compute):
 EC2 is a web service which provides resizable 
  - Insance launch, creating instances, key pairs, security groups

## EC2 insrance creation:
   Requirement gathering
   key pairs
   security group
   instance launch

## EBS(Elastic Block Storage): 
  - virtual hard disk
  - volume, the virtual hasrd disk
  - snapshot - backup & restore

